    description: "Poor top rack cleaning on a Samsung dishwasher is almost always the upper spray arm. In this Chino Hills home, the upper spray arm ports were 80% blocked with mineral deposits — 3 years of hard water without filter cleaning. The pump and motor were fine. We removed and descaled the spray arm assembly, cleaned the filter, and advised on a quarterly filter maintenance schedule. The customer had been about to buy a new dishwasher. Cost: $89 diagnostic + $65 service. Dishwasher restored to like-new cleaning performance. Quarterly filter cleaning in Chino Hills is not optional. It's every 3 months, not annually.",
