  {
    stars: 5,
    text: '"Bosch dishwasher was showing E24 and another company told me I needed a new drain pump. Same Day came out, cleaned the filter and found a kinked hose. $89 and it\'s been running perfect for six months. Really wish I\'d called them first."',
